sequenceDiagram
    participant A as Phone A
    participant Net as Local WiFi
    participant B as Phone B

    Note over A,B: Discovery (automatic)

    A->>Net: mDNS: "I'm Vinay's Pixel<br/>on _merrilin-sync._tcp."
    B->>Net: mDNS: "I'm Vinay's Tab<br/>on _merrilin-sync._tcp."
    Net-->>A: peerDiscovered: Vinay's Tab
    Net-->>B: peerDiscovered: Vinay's Pixel

    Note over A,B: Pairing (user-initiated)

    A->>A: Display QR code<br/>(endpoint + fingerprint)
    B->>A: Scan QR → POST /api/local-sync/pair<br/>{ code, my fingerprint }
    A-->>B: { your shared secret,<br/>my fingerprint }

    Note over A,B: Both store:<br/>fingerprint + shared secret<br/>Trust established
